values: I know I've probably done this a lot, but new journal. Should be writing in it regularly. Hopefully

God is so amazing. After days of hearing about my parent's coming separation and him planning to go to Argentina to see some fat ass ex-girlfriend, and thinking we'd have to move to Florida, we are now coming up with ways for us to stay home. Things are going to be ok, hopefully.

My folks are splitting up most likely.
Worst comes to worst we're moving to Florida to move with my uncle.
I'm taking it upon myself to find my mom a decent paying full-time job and/or somewhere cheaper to live

weird, i went on AIM today for the first time in a month.
ps my new screen name is HOLLA lucas

and the oc was intense tonight, pretty happy about trey leaving but still, he got shot

I've been such a hermit lately. I haven't been on AIM in like a month. Myspace just once in a while (to read comments and messages I usually don't get.) Livejournal to view friends' posts. Weird.
